Sometimes it is hard to like things, most of the time I can do it normally, but sometime thing just don't have taste at all, I really like a lot of things, but when I'm like that, I can't do anything, and with time, I just learn to not spoil things, to just wait till the feeling is out. Otherwise, I can just start to hate a lot of stuff.
For me, polyamory is super important, not just in my romantic life, but I am one of those people who don't have a favorite movie, books or song, as I said with the fruit salad different kind of things give me a different kind of feeling, so I can't just ''chose'' choosing is too painful when there is so much great things around here

I always wonder what I could to today\n\nif I want to do [[something]] I love I will have to be very busy not to think of everything else\n\nWhy it is so complicated\n\nMy head is like full, but I have to make it [[empty]] especialy if I want to do something people want me to do.
I just started this new video game it took me like three [[day to choose]] now I can't think about anything else. \nIt's great, Hope I didn't have a bad time while [[waiting to sleep tonight]] like it happen a lot when something is inside my head too much, I just can't past to all the things' society want me to do.
A lot of the time, I am just waiting to sleep in my bed. Sometime for a really long time, it is almost one of the few cases for me of waiting who is not painful. Waiting for almost every other things is really complicated.\n\nEven when I am waiting to sleep, I don't "wait", I prefer to let my mind wander around, [[in different worlds]]. Sometime, when I am done for waiting, I just get up in the middle of the night and start to [[do things]] again
Thoses are the best and the worst I can do an impressive amount of things for the current hyperfixation, but they are realy hard to control either to do something else when one occure or to know for what subject the next one will be. So it is a dangerous gambling. I'm lucky, beacause most of the time, I manage to make theme work for me, like with [[video game programming]]
Currently, I'm a transgirl btw.\nDoes it have to be with [[autism|autistic]], I don't know, I don't think so, or not in the way you can think of. I don't see the world like most of the people around here. So maybe it helped me don't see myself the way everyone sees me ..?\n\n<span class="smallerImage">\n[img[feebc576e31c9a180727bf58b1997cfd]]\n</span>
Talking about chemistry, I have a lot to take every day. Right now, has I write this line, I remember to take some of them this [[morning]]. I have to take some in the morning. Some at night, some when I think about them, for my eyes, for my lunge, for [[my body shape]], I don't have an important sickness, but I have an impressive amount of piles to take for someone who is not [[sick]].
I do my best to not be rude or meane with people, it leads me to apologize a lot and overexplain a lot, like ''a lot''. I overexplain all the time for anything because, I like people to overexplain. Not everything, but for all social stuff, please, overexplain to me, I'll never get it otherwise.\n\nI also give a lot of compliemnt, beacause I whant people to know when I [[liked]] something.
Lots of game share a common base sometime it is the interaction between the player and the game, sometimes it is like the whole story or the gameplay but, a lot of the time, when I start a game, a new game, after an hour or so it feels like I have [[already played]] it
I already said I love [[video game]] somewhere, but programming, it has come from a simple fact "I think so much about game, I should make some myself", and then it started, I learn it alone, in the beginning on GameMakerStudio 2, then Unity, I'm quite fascinated about it, I love to make thing, see them work and try to make people feel something with it. When I started to do art, I was not quite sure how to put all my political view into my medium, at the time sculpting, but  with video game, I can put as much of [[feminism|Feminist]] as I want into it ! 
My feminism is intersectional btw, if your feminism doesn't involve trans, poor, black people, etc and how domination work when you take all of them at once it is not feminism. Systemic oppression work by addition, it would be great if every problem was not connected.
Do you know about masking ? It is when you have to hide something, but like a personality trait, it happens a lot for little girls, because society tells her how to be and not to be (it happens for boys to, but because I'm a girl I won't talk about it) it is the reason why girl are not diagnosed with autism, because they are so good at hiding things that doctor don't see "classic" as in "boys" autistic traits. So it can take a lot of time. \n\nFor me, it is still a bit difficult, [[I'm a trans girl|my gender]] so, when I see a doctor for autism problem, they don't understand that if I have to grow pretending to be another gender, I ''may as well'' hide the fact that I'm autistic. Lots of the time they don't event understand what is a trans person anyway
Some people say I'm an avatar of chaos, but it is so not true, I have so many unspoken rules. Many of them are really arbitrary for neurotypical and that is the only reason they think I am chaotic. It only [[seems]] like I do random things.\n\n<span class="smallerImage">\n[img[1920px-neurodiversity_symbol.svg]]\n</span>
Everything is so slow[[....]]
When I have first studied video game, I learn from Jason Vanderberg, a brilliant researcher in video game theory, than most people have 2 favorite video game gender and don't play more than four or five different type of game. What a surprise, I guess I don't play all the type of game all the time and some are my "favorite", but I play all theme ... 
I hate beaying sick, most of the time it is realy anoying, but, it mean one of my [[boyfriends]] to take care of me so [[....]]
I don't know what is the things between me and this medium. But, I am ''so impacted'' by it, give me a great emotional game and I will cry a lot. Put me in front of an intense combat game and I will be so ecstatic. Give me a really hard platform game, like Celeste, I can do 600 try just to finish one lvl. Give me the most stupid, goofiest game I will be so entertained. [[All game have a place in my heart]], even the terrible one, sometime, I like to play a bad game, to see how I can still have fun with theme. Something I feel really true for me, creativity come from restriction, and video game are a great way to both give opportunity and restrict.\n\nOh, I'm [[autistic]] by the way

I can't take my time, I simply can't, everything have to be fast, when I'm around other people I always node when I get the point hoping for the person to stop there and move on. That is so amazing, and it seems so relaxing. For a lot of [[autistic]] people, we just guess by trial and error what you were about to say

Someday, when I can't sleep, but I know ''I have to'' I try to take really long respiration & count theme, most of the time, I have already lost count for thinking about something else around the 3rd. For those who are not [[polyamorous]], it is a great metaphor. The thing is, your relationships are like fruits. If you like fruits, it doesn't mean you have to love all of them (this part is for the people who think that because people are poly, mean they are interested in you ... ''spoiler'' if you think that, they are not into you) but, you can found one two, three fruits you love equally, sometime you are more into banana, or oranges, but almost all the time, you don't stop to love oranges. Furthermore, (English is not even my native language, but I know what I'm doing by using this word) an orange are always better at being an orange than a banana and a banana is a better banana than an orange. It can be stupid said like this, but it means that you love each of your partners for a different reason and because they are not the same. All are fruits, not all of them are at your taste, but each is great and different.
